spec_data.Name: kf5-libkipi
spec_data.Description:
Kipi (KDE Image Plugin Interface) is an effort to develop a common plugin
structure (for Digikam, Gwenview, etc.). Its aim is to share
image plugins among graphic applications.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 04 Oct 2017 11:48:06 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Common plugin infrastructure for KDE image applications
